videos.headline: Samson Nacua goes airborne to make TD catch for BYU
videos.description: Jaren Hall lets it fly toward the end zone, where Samson Nacua wins the jump ball and comes down with a BYU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Samson Nacua goes airborne to make TD catch for BYU) 2021/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boise State scores after forcing BYU fumble
